(a) Where leave from work is required, an employee shall be entitled to special leave at their regular 
rate of pay for the following: 
(1) wedding of the employee - two days; 
(2) attend wedding of the employee's child - one day; 
(3) birth of the employee's child - two days; 
(4) serious household or domestic emergency - one day;
